Interface MavenModelPatterns

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractMavenModelPatterns, DefaultProjectParentPatterns, DefaultTopReactorPatterns

    public interface MavenModelPatterns
    Holder specification for Patterns intended to validate or invalidate data retrieved from a Maven POM.
    Author:
    Lennart Jörelid, jGuru Europe AB
